quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  79,1,Ndarahiye kuri ba bamarayika bakwega n’inguvu imitima y’abantu babi
  79,2,No kuri barya bakura imitima y’abantu beranda n’ubwitonzi ntangere
  79,3,No kuri barya bogana niyo mitima bayitwara ningoga na ningoga
  79,4,N’ukuyi shikana n’ingoga na n’ingoga iyo bayishikana
  79,5,N’ukuzigirira ibikenewe kuriyo
  79,6,Umusi izovuzwa inzamba yambere ikazojugumiza ibintu vyose
  79,7,Hanyuma hakurikire inzamba igira kabiri
  79,8,Kuri uwo musi imitima y’abantu izo diha diha kubera ubwoba
  79,9,Amaso yayo azoba yunamye hasi
  79,10,"Abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri bazo vuga bati:- mbega ni vy’ukuri twebwe tuzosubizwa nk’uko twari tumeze aho hambere"
  79,11,Naho twoba turi amagufa masa yamaze kuribwa hagati yayo
  79,12,"Bazo\tvuga\tnkaba\ttyoza\taya\tmajambo\tbati:-\tingaruka\ty’ibi\tvyose n’uruhombo kuri twebwe"
  79,13,Mu vy’ukuri uwo musi w’imperuka uzobaho hakubiswe akaruru kamwe gusa
  79,14,Mu mwanya abantu bose bazoba bari kw’Isi nshasha
  79,15,Mbega uramaze gushikirwa n’inkuru y’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii)
  79,16,"Mugihe\tUmuremyi\twiwe\tyamuhamagarira\tmu\tmwaba\tmutagatifu witiriwe Twuwa"
  79,17,"Imubwira\titi:-\tn’ugende\tkwa\tFir’auni,\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tniwe\tyimonogoje n’ubwishime bwiwe"
  79,18,"Umubwire uti:- mbega wewe ugomba kwisukura"
  79,19,Nanje nzokurongora ku Muremyi wawe kugira ngo uyi gamburukire
  79,20,Rero yaramweretse ibimenyetso bikuru bikuru
  79,21,Mugabo kuri ivyo vyose yarabi hakanye ariyonkora
  79,22,Mu nyuma yarasubiye inyuma atangura kwihangana kugira ngo azitire abantu ntibakurikire intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii)
  79,23,Yarakoranije abantu abahamagara
  79,24,"Avuga ati :- ni jewe Muremyi wanyu mukuru"
  79,25,Aho niho Imana yamufata mukuboko kwiwe mukuriha kumvugo yiwe ya nyuma hamwe n’imvugo yiwe yambere
  79,26,Mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo utuzwa kuri bamwe batinya Imana yabo y’ukuri